{"id":583365,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/04/人民网-女研究生发布精日反华言论-厦大：将/","date":"2018-04-23T06:13:27Z","modified":"2018-04-23T06:13:27Z","title":"人民网 | 女研究生发布“精日反华言论” 厦大：将严肃处理","content":"<p>据厦门大学官微消息，厦门大学就网名为“洁洁良”的微博用户在网上发表错误言论一事作出回应。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/6044f37f78b34ef18a74cd196ebcf814.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-583366\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/6044f37f78b34ef18a74cd196ebcf814.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"493\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/6044f37f78b34ef18a74cd196ebcf814.jpeg 898w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/6044f37f78b34ef18a74cd196ebcf814-300x247.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/6044f37f78b34ef18a74cd196ebcf814-768x631.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>我校高度重视关于网友反映的网名为“洁洁良”的微博用户在网上发表错误言论一事,马上成立工作组进行调查。经查,该微博用户为我校环境与生态学院在读研究生。目前,学校已启动相关处理程序,将依纪依规对该生进行严肃的党纪校纪处理。</p>\n<p>学校将以此为戒,加强对学生的教育,严格学生党员的日常教育管理。感谢广大网友对厦门大学长期以来的关注和监督!</p>\n<p>厦门大学</p>\n<p>2018.4.21</p>\n<p><strong>相关回顾:</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/01ceb678f44b443bbd67a88452af3f0d.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-583367\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/01ceb678f44b443bbd67a88452af3f0d.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/01ceb678f44b443bbd67a88452af3f0d.jpeg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/01ceb678f44b443bbd67a88452af3f0d-169x300.jpeg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/622715461ef6415a86b8b9ab9422e0e5.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-583368\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/622715461ef6415a86b8b9ab9422e0e5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"620\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/622715461ef6415a86b8b9ab9422e0e5.jpeg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/622715461ef6415a86b8b9ab9422e0e5-213x300.jpeg 213w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/60718250ly1fqknqzpszzj20ew0msgzm.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-583369\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/60718250ly1fqknqzpszzj20ew0msgzm.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"601\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/60718250ly1fqknqzpszzj20ew0msgzm.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/04/60718250ly1fqknqzpszzj20ew0msgzm-220x300.jpg 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20505],"tags":[21118,14541,34423,34424,34089,9212]}